{"tid":1079697,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［推普］澳門 資助 葡萄牙學校 推「普通話培訓」","createTime":"2019-03-27T06:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T17:43:28.000Z","uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c6d12a3c4b577c88fedd8be8f15c522512ae529e","tid":1079697,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:04:25.000Z","msg":"澳門社會文化司司長譚俊榮接受《平台》訪問時稱，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">澳門特區政府希望為葡萄牙的中文教師提供更多普通話培訓</span></strong>，以及為澳門教師提供更多葡語培訓。並表示「澳門有6,700名中學生學習葡語」。<br />\n<br />\n譚俊榮並將與葡萄牙教育部部長羅德里格斯 (Tiago Brand&atilde;o Rodrigues) 簽署締結姐妹學校協議書，來自葡萄牙學校有五間，澳門的學校則有三間，這幾間姐妹學校已經分別<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">教授普通話</span></strong>及葡語。<br />\n<br />\n據有關協議，澳門濠江中學、青州小學、坊眾學校、聖若瑟教區中學和高美士中葡中學，與葡萄牙布拉加市的Carlos Amarante學校、馬托西紐什市的Augusto Gomes學校、聖若昂-達馬德拉市的Oliveira J&uacute;nior學校、大馬里尼亞市的Eng&ordm; Calazans Duarte學校及科英布拉市的D. Duarte 學校締結為姐妹學校。並以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">葡語、普通語和英語作為交流活動的使用語言</span></strong>。"},{"pid":"85de98632717fc1157701d47dfad5e26a0913984","tid":1079697,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:05:50.000Z","msg":"<ins><a href=\"https://www.plataformamedia.com/zh-tw/要聞/社會/interior/amp/澳門擴大資助普通話在葡國發展-10559040.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.plataformamedia.com%2Fzh-tw%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%2Finterior%2Famp%2F%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%E5%9C%A8%E8%91%A1%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95-10559040.html&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5W2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=ba6e55b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.plataformamedia.com/zh-tw/要聞/社會/interior/amp/澳門擴大資助普通話在葡國發展-10559040.html</a></ins>"},{"pid":"9aa898a89c3b130c37a6f164bb1d0d71df50a1f3","tid":1079697,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:11:49.000Z","msg":"教育部國務秘書助理Alexandra Leit&atilde;o強調，「近年來，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">提供普通話教學的葡萄牙學校</span></strong>，與教授葡文的澳門學校之間的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">夥伴關係邁出重要一步</span></strong>。」且協議中的五間葡萄牙學校均是來自不同地區。<br />\n<br />\n教育領域是譚俊榮此次到訪葡萄牙的重點行程，並於13日回澳。這次訪問<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">為中葡建交40年周年和澳門主權移交中國20周年慶祝的一部分</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.globalnoticias.pt/pg/image.aspx?brand=PG&amp;type=generate&amp;guid=98bfe6b7-b866-4c24-bdef-b73d9ba07bcf&amp;w=579&amp;h=371&amp;t=20190209073659\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.globalnoticias.pt%2Fpg%2Fimage.aspx%3Fbrand%3DPG%26type%3Dgenerate%26guid%3D98bfe6b7-b866-4c24-bdef-b73d9ba07bcf%26w%3D579%26h%3D371%26t%3D20190209073659&h=5b341dd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n譚俊榮在3月11日亦會再次到訪葡萄牙，接受里斯大學所頒發的榮譽博士學位，表揚他為葡萄牙語言及文化教育發展做出貢獻。"},{"pid":"30f04252d58ffd7d9e731a6dc750b1f6ee94717b","tid":1079697,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:13:21.000Z","msg":"等睇佢上葡廣視果條柒片"},{"pid":"36c2bb7fda2a7c37089851c6489c036083a1e446","tid":1079697,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:35:32.000Z","msg":"叫左崔世安培訓普通話先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0dec253d30044eb0af710ff5897fb4801be82a","tid":1079697,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:35:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca4a413efebc1df387773ca4e460e3461c8b71d5","tid":1079697,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:43:28.000Z","msg":"其實澳門人識葡文真係搵到食架？<br />\n會有好大優勢？<br />\n<br />\n除咗做政府或者law之外仲有咩用"}]}